315
00:25:29,480 --> 00:25:31,859
[SPEAKER_00] plamen te neće opaliti.

316
00:25:33,420 --> 00:25:34,519
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ja sam Jahve,

317
00:25:34,519 --> 00:25:35,819
[SPEAKER_00] bog tvoj,

318
00:25:35,819 --> 00:25:37,920
[SPEAKER_00] svetac Izraelov,

319
00:25:37,920 --> 00:25:40,140
[SPEAKER_00] tvoj spasitelj,

320
00:25:40,140 --> 00:25:43,640
[SPEAKER_00] za otkupninu tvoju dajem Egipat,

321
00:25:43,640 --> 00:25:47,759
[SPEAKER_00] mjesto tebe dajem kuš i šebu.

322
00:25:47,759 --> 00:25:55,259
[SPEAKER_04] Na radiju su stalno bile pjesme domoljubne,

323
