[SPEAKER_03] ali je pedesetak momaka poginulo u tom ratu,

336
00:26:35,400 --> 00:26:36,019
[SPEAKER_03] sigurno.

337
00:26:36,019 --> 00:26:37,480
[SPEAKER_03] Tako da,

338
00:26:37,480 --> 00:26:39,619
[SPEAKER_03] to su bili njihovi očevi,

339
00:26:39,619 --> 00:26:41,259
[SPEAKER_03] njihovi prijatelji

340
00:26:41,259 --> 00:26:46,720
