341
00:26:47,079 --> 00:26:48,980
[SPEAKER_03] ja sam dobila popodnevnu smjenu,

342
00:26:48,980 --> 00:26:52,680
[SPEAKER_03] šesta šesteta da je imala, to je bio moj prvi radni dan,

343
00:26:52,680 --> 00:26:56,819
[SPEAKER_03] bili su skračeni satovi na 35 minuta,

344
00:26:56,819 --> 00:27:00,400
